--- In nbwrpg@y..., "dcoburn" <dcoburn@n...> wrote:
> ::Orchestra::
> 
>        Orchestra sighed.
> 
>         "See, I came to this planet with my brothers.  I landed 
inside this
> volcano, and when I came out of my pod, I couldn't see my brothers 
anywhere.
> Before I go any further, my brothers are named Composer and 
Symphony.  We
> were supposed to be together, but somehow we got separated.  So I 
thought,
> that maybe I should join a faction, and if I ever find my brothers, 
I can
> make them join my faction and we can be together like we are 
supposed to,"
> He explained.
